#Question6-How do you extract the string ‘Worl’ from the above string using negative index?
strr = "Hello World"
print(strr[-5:-1])

#Question7-Reverse the string “5+6*3-45”. The output should be “45-3*6+5”.
a="5+6*3-45"
print(a[::-1])

